OL,3,CLittle Mix star Perrie Edwards reveals
OL,4,Cpain of two miscarriages
OL,6,FSpeaking on the We Need To Talk
OL,7,Fpodcast with Paul C Brunson, 32-year-
OL,8,Fold Edwards said her first miscarriage
OL,9,Fbefore the birth of her son Axel in
OL,10,F2021, occurred very early in the
OL,11,Fpregnancy.
OL,13,F"I remember finding out I was
OL,14,Fpregnant. Obviously, I started
OL,15,Fbleeding not long after, and I went to
OL,16,Fhospital and I had the scan and they
OL,17,Fwere like, 'There's no baby.'
OL,19,F"And I was like, 'Oh, I've made this
OL,20,Fup. Maybe I got a false positive or
OL,21,Fsomething'.
