OL,3,CLittle Mix star Perrie Edwards reveals
OL,4,Cpain of two miscarriages
OL,6,F"I was rehearsing for the last Little
OL,7,FMix tour, and I thought, 'I don't feel
OL,8,Fgood'. Every symptom under the sun. I
OL,9,Fwas like, 'I think I'm pregnant,'" she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FBut by 24 weeks, after Edwards had
OL,13,Fstarted planning the baby's nursery,
OL,14,Fdoctors told the couple the baby had
OL,15,Fno heartbeat, in what the singer said
OL,16,Fwas the "worst day of my life".
OL,18,FShe said: "It's weird, because the
OL,19,Ffirst time it happened, I think
OL,20,Fbecause it was so early, I was like,
OL,21,F'Oh, that's hard'.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
