OL,6,F"But I think when you're 24 weeks and
OL,7,Fyou've planned out their room and all
OL,8,Fthese things, it's really hard. And
OL,9,Fnobody knows other than immediate
OL,10,Ffriends and family."
OL,12,FEdwards has been with former Liverpool
OL,13,Fand Arsenal midfielder Oxlade-
OL,14,FChamberlain since 2017 and they became
OL,15,Fengaged in 2022, the same year Little
OL,16,FMix went on hiatus and around the time
OL,17,FEdwards suffered her second
OL,18,Fmiscarriage.
